        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "She continued, It hath reached me, O auspicious King, that the bondmaid sent by Hayat al Nufus made her way to Ardashir and delivered him her lady's message, which when he heard, he wept with sore weeping and said to her, \"Know that Hayat al Nufus is my mistress and that I am her slave and the captive of her love.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
