        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "He rose up standing and received him with honour; but the Minister made haste to fall at his feet and kissing them cried, \"Pardon, O King of the Age!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
