        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "They spread the marriage feasts and banquets and lastly Ardashir went in unto the Princess and found her a jewel which had been hidden, an union pearl unthridden and a filly that none but he had ridden, so he notified this to his sire.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
