        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "After this he returned to his capital and Ardashir and his company fared on, till they reached Shiraz, where they celebrated the marriage festivities anew.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
