        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "And they abode in all comfort and solace and joyance of life, till there came to them the Destroyer of delights and Severer of societies; the Depopulator of palaces and the Garnerer of graveyards.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
