        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "I couldn't think of spending any of it.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8347_282412_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8347/282412/8347_282412_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "The stranger picked up a large stone and threw it into the hole.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8347_282412_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8347/282412/8347_282412_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "\"If that is the case,\" he said, \"cover up that stone.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8347_282412_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8347/282412/8347_282412_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "It is worth just as much to you as the treasure you lost!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8347_282412_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8347/282412/8347_282412_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "THE WOLF AND THE HOUSE DOG",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8347_282412_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8347/282412/8347_282412_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "There was once a Wolf who got very little to eat because the Dogs of the village were so wide awake and watchful.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8347_282412_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8347/282412/8347_282412_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "He was really nothing but skin and bones, and it made him very downhearted to think of it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8347_282412_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8347/282412/8347_282412_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "One night this Wolf happened to fall in with a fine fat House Dog who had wandered a little too far from home.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8347_282412_000025_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8347/282412/8347_282412_000025_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "So the Wolf spoke very humbly to the Dog, complimenting him on his fine appearance.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8347_282412_000026_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8347/282412/8347_282412_000026_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "Why, you have to fight hard for every bite you get.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8347_282412_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8347/282412/8347_282412_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "\"What must I do?\" asked the Wolf.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8347_282412_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8347/282412/8347_282412_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "\"Hardly anything,\" answered the House Dog.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8347_282412_000028_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8347/282412/8347_282412_000028_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "\"Chase people who carry canes, bark at beggars, and fawn on the people of the house.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8347_282412_000028_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8347/282412/8347_282412_000028_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "In return you will get tidbits of every kind, chicken bones, choice bits of meat, sugar, cake, and much more beside, not to speak of kind words and caresses.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8347_282412_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8347/282412/8347_282412_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "The Wolf had such a beautiful vision of his coming happiness that he almost wept.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8347_282412_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8347/282412/8347_282412_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "\"What is that on your neck?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8347_282412_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8347/282412/8347_282412_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "\"Nothing at all,\" replied the Dog.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8347_282412_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8347/282412/8347_282412_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "\"What! nothing!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8347_282412_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8347/282412/8347_282412_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "\"But please tell me.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8347_282412_000035_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8347/282412/8347_282412_000035_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "\"Perhaps you see the mark of the collar to which my chain is fastened.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8347_282412_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8347/282412/8347_282412_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "\"What!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8347_282412_000036_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8347/282412/8347_282412_000036_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "A chain!\" cried the Wolf.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8347_282412_000036_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8347/282412/8347_282412_000036_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "\"Don't you go wherever you please?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8347_282412_000037_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8347/282412/8347_282412_000037_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "\"Not always!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8347_282412_000037_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8347/282412/8347_282412_000037_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "But what's the difference?\" replied the Dog.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8347_282412_000038_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8347/282412/8347_282412_000038_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "\"All the difference in the world!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8347_282412_000038_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8347/282412/8347_282412_000038_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8347",
        "content": "I don't care a rap for your feasts and I wouldn't take all the tender young lambs in the world at that price.\" And away ran the Wolf to the woods.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
